---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Cookie Policy — Tony Ciencia" description="Tony Ciencia LLC Cookie Policy — what cookies we use and how to manage them.">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-inner">
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>

      <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small text files that websites store on your device when you visit them. They allow the site to remember your preferences and improve your experience.</p>

      <h2>2. Cookies We Use</h2>
      <p><strong>Strictly necessary cookies:</strong> essential for the site to function (e.g., remembering your light/dark theme preference). These do not require your consent.</p>
      <p><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> we collect usage data anonymously to understand how visitors interact with the site and improve it. These are only activated if you accept analytics cookies.</p>

      <h2>3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
      <p>Some embedded content (YouTube videos, third-party forms) may set their own cookies. We do not control these cookies; please refer to each provider's privacy policy.</p>

      <h2>4. Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p>You can accept or reject analytics cookies through the cookie banner that appears on your first visit. You can also configure your browser to block or delete cookies, though this may affect site functionality.</p>

      <h2>5. Consent</h2>
      <p>By clicking "Accept" on the cookie banner, you consent to the use of analytics cookies as described in this policy. You can withdraw your consent at any time through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>6. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about our cookie policy: <a href="mailto:contact@tonyciencia.com">contact@tonyciencia.com</a></p>

      <p class="legal-reviewed">Last reviewed: May 6, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: var(--spacing-16) var(--spacing-6); }
  .legal-inner { max-width: var(--content-width); margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-inner h1 { font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); }
  .legal-inner h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: 600; margin-top: var(--spacing-10); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .legal-reviewed { margin-top: var(--spacing-12); font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--color-muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-top: var(--spacing-4); }
</style>
